<DATE>
<P>
August 23, 1994, Tuesday, Home Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Metro; Part B; Page 7; Column 1; Op-Ed Desk 
</P>
</SECTION>
<LENGTH>
